thread.title: Mrs Collins

author: Mrs Collins
title: Mrs Collins
text: Not in use yet as still awaiting babies arrival but from what we have seen it's fantastic value for money. Very quick delivery too. We live in England and ordered on the Wednesday and it arrived the following Monday. The quality seems great, it is very light and exceptionally easy to fold. Everything you need in one package. Baby bag is quite small though, considering all you need to carry but it will hold the essentials.
